textChapter[0].push("你來到了奧庫茲村。\n一切對你來說都是陌生的。\n讓我們從頭開始學習吧……");
textChapter[1].push("你很快熟悉了這裏的一切。\n是時候開始你的旅程了……\n幫助村民，接受他們的任務。\n你將會獲取他們的信任。…");
textChapter[2].push("你向大家證明了你的能力。\n村民希望得到你的更多幫助。\n通過做任務，你的能力得到更大的提升，\n也會獲取更多有關這次異常的線索。");
textChapter[3].push("你成為了村民們的朋友。\n他們的前程命運靠你去改變了……");
textChapter[4].push("黎明前最黑暗的時刻到來了。\n真相將一個接一個在你眼前揭示。\n勇敢些，你一定會贏得最後的勝利！");
textEx[0].push("喲，你就是那個不安分的，四處給我們添亂的人類嗎？");
textEx[1].push("我等了你好久了。悶在這裏，每次都會聽說你破壞我們計畫的故事呢！真是讓人手癢癢的，有一種將你捏碎的衝動呢！");
textEx[2].push("雙頭巨人？你要見我們老大？哈哈哈哈，你能見到我就很不錯了！好了……你的腳步就在我這裏永遠停住吧！受死吧！");
textEx[3].push("呵呵，你終於出現了。我們就是雙頭巨人，哥哥裏歐和弟弟布朗。");
textEx[4].push("一段時間以前，就聽說有一個和我們作對的人類出現。一直想見見到底是個什麼樣的角色，原來就是這樣一個黃毛小子啊。");
textEx[5].push("不過你還挺有能耐的，每次都成功破壞了我們的計畫呢。看在你能力的份上，我們就不殺你，允許你加入我們，一起復活深淵魔王，這樣你也可以得到永恆的生命了。怎麼樣啊？");
textEx[6].push("不願意嗎？呵呵，那一切就到這裏為止了。我會殺掉你，紮克領主會開啟地下城，黑暗會重新籠罩大地，人類將痛不欲生，我們會獲得永恆的生命……！多麼美好的世界啊！");
textEx[7].push("永別了，你就在這裏變成肉泥吧！");
textEx[8].push("怎麼會！怎麼會變成這樣！我居然被你給打敗了！不要……不要！不要！！你奪去了我的永生！篡改了讓黑暗再次籠罩大地的歷史時刻！為什麼會變成這樣！");
textEx[9].push("不會的……這一切不會就這麼結束的！還有紮克領主在！還有更多魔物在不斷蘇醒……這片大陸終有一日還是會被黑暗佔領的！哈哈哈哈哈……！");
textEx[10].push("我沒有守護好地下城入口的鑰匙……我的使命就到這裏為止了……人類啊，等待你的……是更多的未知數啊……！");
textEx[11].push("很久很久以前，Sakara大陸富足而興旺。在這塊大陸的西邊有一個村莊，叫做奧庫茲。人們在這個村莊裏快樂而安詳地生活著。舒適的生活讓他們漸漸開始忘記那段黑暗的日子：深淵魔王賽巴從地下鑽出來，四處作惡，讓恐怖和悲傷籠罩整個大地……多虧了一群勇士，歷經艱苦的戰鬥，賽巴才被打敗並封印在了地下城的最深處……");
textEx[12].push("最近一段時間，奧庫茲村出現了一些異常。村莊周圍開始出現大量的魔物，動物也變得狂躁不安並開始攻擊人類。許多村民不得不離開村莊，但還是有一部分人留了下來，他們期待著英雄的出現，期待著黎明的到來。");
textEx[13].push("你，英雄的後代，一位冒險家，在聽說了這件事之後，來到了奧庫茲村一探究竟。我們的故事就從這裏展開……");
textNpcName[0].push("Wayne (Village Head)");
textNpcName[1].push("Gran (Blacksmith)");
textNpcName[2].push("Susan (Witch)");
textNpcName[3].push("Chung (Merchant)");
textNpcName[4].push("Paul (Sorehead Knight)");
textNpcName[5].push("Anna (Little Girl)");
textNpcName[6].push("Kimura (Ranger)");
textNpc1[0].push("Welcome to Village Arcuz, young man. I\'m Wayne, the head of this village. It is a long time since an explorer has been here. It seems my invocation last night worked… for real! I\'m glad you\'ve come.");
textNpc1[1].push("When I was a kid, Village Arcuz was the most peaceful village of this land. People here lived very happy lives.");
textNpc1[2].push("The village belongs to landlord Zack, who I am chamberlain for. He is a man with high aspirations and the village flourished thanks to him.");
textNpc1[3].push("But a year ago landlord Zack hide himself in his house to do some kind of research and has not come out since. A huge number of monsters have appeared on the lands surrounding the village since then and have gone wild, attacking and killing villagers and leaving many missing. A lot of people have now left to escape this disaster.");
textNpc1[4].push("Now you know a bit about this village you can start your investigation. Walk around, talk with the villagers. When they got excalmatory mark (!) on their head, help them solve their problems. There may be clues hiding in villagers\' missions which will lead you to find out what happened in this village …");
textNpc1[5].push("Be careful when fighting with the monsters, as you will meet stronger ones during your adventure…");
textNpc1[6].push("I have seen many adventures. Your eyes told me that you are special…I believe you will do great things.");
textNpc1[7].push("Along long time ago, there was a huge war on this land. During the battles, Light defeated Darkness with difficulty. Devil Ssyba was sealed in by warriors and mages deeply and solidly.");
textNpc1[8].push("I heard that the dungeon where Devil Ssyba was sealed in is near this village. But a long time has passed since then and right now no one can find it. I\'m not sure if this time the abnormity has something to do with Devil Ssyba…");
textNpc1[9].push("Landlord Zack is very knowledgeable. He knows many ancient conjurations. He used to come and spend time in this village, and really cared about the villagers but I haven\'t seen him since he locked himself in his house and started doing research. It is forbidden to enter his castle, even to me, his chamberlain…");
textNpc1[10].push("Did you notice that when you are level-up, new battle skills can be learned? You click the SKILL button on the bottom of your screen and distribute your ability points (AP) to the skills on the skill tree. And have you seen the skill shortcut grid on the bottom also? Before fighting, you can put your skills there and press I/L to use them.");
textNpc1[11].push("Battle skill consumes your skill point, which is the green bar below your red HP bar. You can drink the blue potion to get refreshment.");
textNpc1[12].push("Thank you very much indeed for bringing Anna back! She usually behaves like this… Seems she won\'t stop unless she finds her parents…");
textNpc1[13].push("Getting familiar with this land, young man? If you still have questions and difficulties, just keep trying different ways to solve them. Trying is half the fun.");
textNpc1[14].push("By helping the villagers, you have got some clues about the abnormity, haven\'t you? Please continue and help rid us of our troubles forever. …");
textNpc1[15].push("You have been giving the villagers a lot of help these past days. It seems they all treat you as a trusted friend now! Thank you very much indeed, young man!");
textNpc1[16].push("I keep dreaming the same nightmare recently: The ground in the village ruptured and the evil came out from the darkness, which slowly swallowed all the land... Every time I woke up with a start…What\'s the meaning of this nightmare…?");
textNpc1[17].push("…What happened to this village, and what is happening now…?!");
textNpc1[18].push("My nightmare has become reality…I can\'t believe the entrance of the dungeon is actually inside the village…! I have been living here since I was a kid. I always thought it was just a normal village. I never thought there was such a big secret hidden here…");
textNpc1[19].push("Maybe the warriors who sealed Devil Ssyba didn\'t want darkness to return again so they hid the location of the dungeon…");
textNpc1[20].push("So landlord Zack wants to betray the whole land in exchange for immortality? So he really doesn\'t care about his people then? I may be his chamberlain but I had no idea…!");
textNpc1[21].push("The Situation has got so bad and I have inescapable responsibility…Young man, it\'s with your help that we have discovered the truth of this affair.");
textNpc1[22].push("Things are getting tougher…I\'m sorry to involve you in all of this…");
textNpc1[23].push("To return peace and happiness to people living on this land, please keep helping us! And please look after yourself!");
textNpc1[24].push("You have come a long way to the village…");
textNpc1[25].push("Let\'s start from speaking with the village head.");
textNpc1[26].push("Walk to the front of the old man and press J to chat. ");
textNpc2[0].push("Hello! I\'m Gran, the blacksmith of this village! ");
textNpc2[1].push("My family have been blacksmiths here for generations. I learned a lot from my father and grandfather and hope my skill exceeds theirs! ");
textNpc2[2].push("Can I…?");
textNpc2[3].push("Head Wayne asked you to come and buy a weapon? Seems you are accepting his commission! Nice one! Here I have 3 types of weapon: falchion, sword and axe. You can choose which one you like. In future you can also buy equipment such as a shield, armor, etc from me!");
textNpc2[4].push("If you need new weapons, please also come here! I will do my best to make good stuff for you! But I\'m not sure if they are as good as those made by my father and grandfather…!");
textNpc2[5].push("Because I was born in the peaceful time, when weapons and armors were not popular or needed, I have no confidence in the battle equipment I have made…I hope I can learn more from my father and grandfather, but they are gone!");
textNpc2[6].push("I still need to practise more on making weapons and armors…I\'m not that confident...But normal tools are totally no problem! This might be the disadvantage of being born in a peaceful age…!");
textNpc2[7].push("You don\'t like my stuff? Or you doubt my handcraft?! I wish my grandfather were alive! He experienced the war age and I heard that he even crafted super weapons for the warriors who were fighting with the evil ones!");
textNpc2[8].push("I\'m trying to make better equipment! I hope my skill shapes up! But compared with my grandfather I\'m sure I have a lot to learn!");
textNpc2[9].push("I heard that element crystals and stones can be added to any weapon or piece of equipment to improve their abilities. That\'s right isn\'t it? I don\'t know how to do it though. You can ask Susan for details! I want to learn it while I\'m free! But can I handle it…?");
textNpc2[10].push("Though I have made so many weapons, I am still a little bit unconfident…! Is this feeling that every blacksmith born in the peaceful age shares? ...");
textNpc2[11].push("Regarding the weapons: weapon, falchion, axe and sword all have their own characters. You can train your skills specifically to suit the weapon you\'d like to use.");
textNpc2[12].push("Weapons and equipment have a limit on the number of times you can ‘compose\'. In other words, if a piece of kit reaches the upper limit for the number of ‘compositions\', it can\'t be ‘composed\' anymore! This is a basic principle of weapon composition and can\'t be avoided. I had assuming it was my fault for dodgy craftsmanship but then I found it was to do with the durability of the gear, crystal and stone. No one can change their nature.");
textNpc2[13].push("Since you have come to the village, I have made a distinct improvement in making weapons and armoury! It is thanks to you frequently visiting my booth! I want to be awarded the Superb Blacksmith prize for he who can forge most exquisite things, but first I have to catch up with my grandfather\'s level of skill. He won the title in his time.");
textNpc2[14].push("Recently a lot of big things have happened! I hope they haven\'t affected our normal people\'s lives! But no matter what is going to happen, I will survive, and keep improving my skill!");
textNpc2[15].push("Sometimes I ask myself: Are weapons the root of evil?! At that time there is a voice inside my heart telling me: If a weapon is used in the right way, it is the root of peace!");
textNpc2[16].push("Hi friend! You want any equipment? Hope you are satisfied by my craftsmanship!");
textNpc3[0].push("Hi. Are you a guest from other places? I can\'t see, but I smelled a different smell of soils from other lands. My name is Susan.");
textNpc3[1].push("Potions? Sure. Take them from my selling grids to your inventory grids. Remember to put them in the shortcut girds before fighting the monsters and press 1/2/3 to use them. I am the apothecary of this village. Whenever you need potions, please come here.");
textNpc3[2].push("Beside the potion of healing, I also sell potion of mana which recovers your SP, and other potions. ");
textNpc3[3].push("I came hear from another land with my husband. He once went on a business trip and never returned. I still haven\'t got any news about him…My eyes turned blind during a horrible affair a few months ago… I never want to recall that time again…");
textNpc3[4].push("Composition gives your stuff extra power! On the other hand, It\'s a very interesting subject! In the future whenever you want to compose, please come to see me and I will always help.");
textNpc3[5].push("You want to compose? No problem, I can help you. Please put the crystals, stone and weapon on the composition panel. When everything\'s ready, just click the COMPOSE button.");
textNpc3[6].push("Are you concerned by something? Blindness made my other senses more sensitive, so I can sense things others can\'t…");
textNpc3[7].push("I think this time the abnormity is not that simple, behind it there may exist a very strong power of evil …");
textNpc3[8].push("My husband and I came from another land. Most people there knew how to make potions and read paternosters. Though I am blind, I can still make very good potions by using my nose and taste.");
textNpc3[9].push("The red potions can recover your health points. The blue ones can recover your skill points. The purple ones can recover both HP and SP. The green ones can detoxify. Apart from these, I have other potions too. Please read their labels before buying them.");
textNpc3[10].push("My eyes were blind months ago. I clearly remember that day, suddenly a group of Centaurs rushed into the village. They lanced on towards me, took my eyes away then swaggered off. They didn\'t attack the other villagers. It seems they came just to take my eyes away…");
textNpc3[11].push("I\'m doing research and hope one day in the future I will be able to see well again.");
textNpc3[12].push("As I told you, I\'m from another land. In our land education is well developed. That\'s why I could read different types of paternosters. Since my eyes were taken away, I have always asked myself the question: Is there anything which they don\'t want me to read?");
textNpc3[13].push("I\'m always talking about myself, sorry. Whether it be weapon, armour or accessories, all of them can be composed with element crystals and stones. Small pieces can be composed into a larger one too. For instance, several small crystals can be composed to a medium one, and several medium ones can turn into a large piece.");
textNpc3[14].push("Moreover, several stones of blessing can be composed into a stone of soul, and stones of soul can be turned into a holy stone. ");
textNpc3[15].push("But, there is not certainty in this. Composition can fail. If a composition progress fails, the materials disappear and you need to go and collect them again.");
textNpc3[16].push("After my eyes were robbed by the Centaurs, I had to get used to the darkness. If I\'m one day able to see again, I may need some time to get use to the light again…hehe…");
textNpc3[17].push("If I\'m able to see, I can read more books and research on more types of potion…Even my husband couldn\'t stop my addiction to the potions…");
textNpc3[18].push("And it is because this land contains abundant elements that we travelled here and settled down…");
textNpc3[19].push("Every morning when my eyes are still closed, I can feel the sunlight outside my window. And then I open my eyes, I see flowers and birds. This feeling is fabulous! Young warrior, I will never forget your help! Anything that I can help, come to me.");
textNpc3[20].push("You can improve the level of your weapons by composing stones with them. A weapon has 5 levels. A higher level indicates higher attributes. 3 different stones together (blessing, soul and holy) can make your weapon level-up once.");
textNpc3[21].push("Apart from main potions like Potion of Healing, Potion of Mana and potion of rejuvenation, I make 5 assistant potions: Potion of Defence, Potion of Attack, Potion of Magic Defence, Potion of Berserk and Potion of Luck. They are used to improve one of your specific capacities during a fixed length of period. If you use them correctly during battle, they could help a lot.");
textNpc3[22].push("I also make Potion of Archangel. After drinking it, when your HP goes down to zero, it revives you once. Isn\'t it amazing?");
textNpc3[23].push("In these tough times, please look after yourself well! I look forward to seeing you return victorious over and over again!");
textNpc3[24].push("Using potions effectively to refresh your HP and SP will be a great help during battle. Before entering any tough battle, using a potion of archangel in advance will help you a lot!");
textNpc3[25].push("Hi, Do you need any help? Potion(J) or Composition(K)? Quit(ESC)");
textNpc4[0].push("Hey young man, do you want to buy something? My stuff is really good but also very expensive! Get lost if you don\'t have the dough. I can\'t stand penniless paupers and don\'t even think about trying to barter!");
textNpc4[1].push("I don\'t accept credit! A long time ago some adventurers bought some of my stuff on credit but then died out in the wild and I lost a packet! That was so painful for me! They didn\'t care about their lives, but I really cared about my fortune!!");
textNpc4[2].push("Money and precious stuff are everything in one\'s life! What? You don\'t agree with me?");
textNpc4[3].push("Business is just getting worse and worse. A year ago, more travellers came to this village in one day then have come in the whole last year. You always come to my booth. To me, you are my VIP customer!");
textNpc4[4].push("I love earning money. If I got something precious at a low price and sell it at a high price then I\'m happy as Larry!");
textNpc4[5].push("Are you coming to my booth less than before? Or it is just my illusion…?");
textNpc4[6].push("You run here and there and help the villagers. Do they pay you for doing this?...What? You\'re doing it for free? You are in no way suited to being a merchant! But…I acknowledge that you are a great adventurer!");
textNpc4[7].push("Everyone says you are a good man, young man! You\'re not doing too bad! Umm…all right! I have decided! From now on, I\'ll give you a 0.01% discount on the stuff you buy from me! Oh how generous I am!!");
textNpc4[8].push("For warriors like you, speed of changing equipment is key – as you always need better gear to satisfy the requirement of fighting with stronger enemies. So when you get gear that you want to get rid of, you can sell it to me! Price is not a problem!");
textNpc4[9].push("Hey, you\'re much busier than before, young man! But don\'t forget to come to my booth regularly!");
textNpc4[10].push("Don\'t die! Without you I have no VIP!");
textNpc4[11].push("Hey young man, do you want to buy something? We have good stuff here!");
textNpc5[0].push("Travelling adventurer…? Hehe…you\'d better leave this land asap…");
textNpc5[1].push("Me? I am just a defeated knight.");
textNpc5[2].push("Excuse me, I don\'t want to talk. Everyday I am living in my nightmare-like memory. I have had enough.");
textNpc5[3].push("How\'s it going young man? If you are not well trained you cannot defeat those strong monsters.");
textNpc5[4].push("I am the captain of a squad that belongs to the royal army of this land. My troops and I came to investigate the abnormity in this village. Then we met a bloody horrible giant. He is so big. He has two heads and his howl made the whole valley shake…");
textNpc5[5].push("He smashed us easily. Only I escaped with my last breath…It was the toughest battle I have ever been in. Every night when I think of my troops I cannot sleep…");
textNpc5[6].push("I feel this time the abnormity is not as simple as before. I can feel behind it there is a very strong dark power swarming. It seems like it could spout out at any moment. Unfortunately, I am too weak to go investigating again…");
textNpc5[7].push("If your inventory is full loaded, you can store the items which are not regularly used in my cases. I will take care of them for you.");
textNpc5[8].push("I feel guilty everyday. I think I am a flunky who dropped his buddies and escaped…I do hope all this is just a nightmare…!");
textNpc5[9].push("My troops died in the wild and cannot lay to rest. As their captain, I really feel sorry to them…");
textNpc5[10].push("My storage cases helped you? I can look after the items which you don\'t want to drop off or are too heavy to put in your inventory.");
textNpc5[11].push("You can buy more storage space. All you need to do is go to the game website and pay by Paypal.");
textNpc5[12].push("About uploading saved files, the advantage is that no matter where or which computer you are using, you can load your personal data and continue the game. This is a charged service too.");
textNpc5[13].push("My heart began to calm down after my troops were laid to rest. Thank you, young warrior. I need to recover my body, and be positive. I hope I can give you more help with your investigation and provide you with clues.");
textNpc5[14].push("Have you handed the letter to Wayne?");
textNpc5[15].push("Take the scroll to Susan and see if she can read it.");
textNpc5[16].push("...");
textNpc5[17].push("Inventory full loaded? Put some in my storage cases and I will take care of them for you!");
textNpc6[0].push("Hi! Your hair is very nice!");
textNpc6[1].push("If you are not busy, play games with me!");
textNpc6[2].push("The knight wearing armor is not as terrible as his word. I saw him crying quietly, all lonely! I thought only Anna cried, but adult cries too!");
textNpc6[3].push("People in this village treat me very well and I\'m very happy, but it doesn\'t stop me missing my mom and dad …!");
textNpc6[4].push("Teddy Bear is Anna\'s best friend. You are Teddy\'s life saver. So you are my best friend too!");
textNpc6[5].push("Help!");
textNpc6[6].push("Anna has a nice dad and a nice mom! Mom is beautiful and she always cooks delicious food for me!");
textNpc6[7].push("Dad is tall and strong. He always picks me up and uses his beard to kiss my face…Although sometimes I\'m angry with them, but right now I really miss them so much!");
textNpc6[8].push("When will mom and dad come back?");
textNpc6[9].push("When Anna grows up, she wants to become a woman as good as Susan!");
textNpc6[10].push("Do you think I am pretty?...Hee hee…");
textNpc6[11].push("Recently Kimura and Paul seem to have changed a lot! I feel they are both happier than before!");
textNpc6[12].push("You seem a little bit tired!");
textNpc6[13].push("Take some rest and play with me for a while!");
textNpc7[0].push("Wow, look! Are you an explorer from far away places? I am also an explorer, I\'m Kimura. You must have heard about me, right? I\'m such a famous adventurer!");
textNpc7[1].push("I once slayed an evil dragon! Its eyes were as big as a cave!... ");
textNpc7[2].push("You don\'t believe me? You really don\'t believe me??");
textNpc7[3].push("Well, forget about it.");
textNpc7[4].push("I once stole God\'s apple! That apple was as big as a mountain! To escape, I had a tough fight with the gods! I defeated them all!");
textNpc7[5].push("What? You don\'t believe me?");
textNpc7[6].push("I\'m not boasting! I\'m from a family of warriors! You wanna take me on?");
textNpc7[7].push("My father and grandfather were both famous warriors! But they are dead! I\'m the only child of my father. He left me a great sword and a martial art book.");
textNpc7[8].push("Actually…it is a little bit embarrassing to say…I arrived at this village with a desire to help the villagers solve the abnormity just like you. But during a battle with Goblins I was defeated.");
textNpc7[9].push("My ancestral sword went missing in that battle, as well as my courage…The monsters are much stronger than I expected…");
textNpc7[10].push("Slayed the evil dragon? Haha! No I didn\'t! That\'s just one of my dreams…I hope one day it comes true!");
textNpc7[11].push("I came to help the village, but I messed it up! I feel ashamed to face the villagers, so I just started boasting the whole time…");
textNpc7[12].push("Carrying the glory of the descendant of warriors, I want to be living an exciting life just like my grandfather and father!");
textNpc7[13].push("But peaceful ages always dilute a fighter\'s enthusiasm…I heard that this village was in trouble. I felt that it was my chance and I came here quickly, but found out I have a long way to go to become a strong warrior…");
textNpc7[14].push("Looking at how active you are makes me excited. I really want to do something to help!");
textNpc7[15].push("Hi buddy! I\'m learning battle skills these days! Come to teach me when you are not busy! Thanks!");
textNpc7[16].push("Living my family glory made me feel a lot more at ease. Right now, I\'m practising hard everyday. A small step forward everyday could be a big step after a few years!");
textNpc7[17].push("It seems an important time is approaching! Don\'t worry about the village, I will protect it with my life! You take care!");
textNpc7[18].push("I still have a long way to go to catch up with you, but compared with myself before I have made great progress! I hope one day I can become your partner and fight together with you under the same sky!");
textQuest1[0].push("As the head of the village, I saw all this happen but cannot do anything to help. I feel terrible about it…Young man, could you please stay here for some days and see if you could help finding some clues?");
textQuest1[1].push("Great, young man! Thank you very much for deciding to help! Here\'s 100 gold. Please go and talk with Gran, the blacksmith at southwest in the village. Buy a weapon, equip it and come back to see me.");
textQuest1[2].push("Ok young man…Please hang around first. I hope later you will change your mind and accept my pleading.");
textQuest1[3].push("Found Blacksmith Gran? His house is at the southwest of the village. Got the weapon and equipped it? You can click the INV button on the bottom of the screen, pick your weapon out from the grid and put it on your body on top of the INV panel.");
textQuest1[4].push("Very good! From the way you are holding the weapon I can see you are an experienced adventurer!");
textQuest1[5].push("Equip a Weapon (Main Quest)");
textQuest1[6].push("Buy a weapon from blacksmith Gran and equip it. Then go to talk with Wayne.");
textQuest2[0].push("There are a loads of monsters outside the village. You need to know how to fight with them. Can you go outside the village and kill 3 Slimes then come back to see me?");
textQuest2[1].push("Good. The village gate is in the south. You attack by pressing key J and jump by pressing key K. You health status is shown at the red bar on the bottom left of the screen. When it turns low, you may die. If that happens, run away from the monsters as far as you can! After killing 3 Slimes please come back to see me.");
textQuest2[2].push("Ok, please look around and prepare yourself well.");
textQuest2[3].push("Outside the village there are green and slimy slimes. Please go out from the south game, find them, kill 3 of them and come back to see me.");
textQuest2[4].push("Well done! It seems you understood how to fight with the monsters. Here\'s 100 gold reward.");
textQuest2[5].push("Kill 3 lv.1 Slime (Main Quest)");
textQuest2[6].push("Kill 3 lv.1 Slime then go back to see Wayne.");
textQuest3[0].push("Next, let\'s try a difficult stuff. When fighting with dozens of monsters, you\'d better use potions to recover your health point. Here\'s 100 gold. Can you go to Susan – the witch there on my left side, buy 5 small potions of healing, kill 10 Slimes and come back to see me?");
textQuest3[1].push("Susan is the apothecary of this village. Her house is at my left side. Please go and talk with her. Before entering the battle field, take your potions out from your inventory (INV) and put them in to the 3 shortcut grids on the bottom of the screen. When your HP is low, you can use the potions by just pressing hotkey 1/2/3. It\'s that easy!");
textQuest3[2].push("Well, please hang around and get yourself well prepared.");
textQuest3[3].push("Killed 10 Slimes? Before entering the battle field, take your potions out and put them in to the 3 shortcut grids on the bottom of the screen. When your HP is low, you can use the potions by just pressing hotkey 1/2/3.");
textQuest3[4].push("Congratulations! You totally got the hang of fighting with the monsters!");
textQuest3[5].push("Kill 10 lv.1 Slimes (Main Quest)");
textQuest3[6].push("Kill 10 lv.1 Slimes then go to talk with Wayne.");
textQuest4[0].push("I also want to tell you something about attribute point and skill point. Have you found that you can level-up after fighting with those Slimes? Every time when you are level-up you get 5 attribute points and 1 skill points.");
textQuest4[1].push("You can click CHAR button on the bottom, distribute the 5 attribute points to your character attributes by clicking the plus button.");
textQuest4[2].push("Also, you can click the SKILL button and add the point to the fighting skills you want to learn/improve. After distributing your points, remember to click the ACCEPT button on the bottom-left of CHAR and SKILL panels. So, you wanna try it now?");
textQuest4[3].push("Please distribute the 5 attribute points and 1 skill point then come to see me again. You can click CHAR button on the bottom, distribute the 5 attribute points to your character attributes by clicking the plus button. Also, you can click the SKILL button and add the point to the fighting skills you want to learn/improve. After distributing your points, remember to click the ACCEPT button on the bottom-left of CHAR and SKILL panels.");
textQuest4[4].push("Ok, come to see me again when you\'ve got it.");
textQuest4[5].push("Got level-up? You can click CHAR button on the bottom, distribute the 5 attribute points to your character attributes by clicking the plus button. Also, you can click the SKILL button and add the point to the fighting skills you want to learn/improve. After distributing your points, remember to click the ACCEPT button on bottom-left of CHAR and SKILL panels.");
textQuest4[6].push("Well done! Your abilities are improved! Here are additional 5 attribute point and 1 skill point as reward to you!");
textQuest4[7].push("Level-up & Skill Point (Main Quest)");
textQuest4[8].push("Distribute 5 attribute points & 1 skill point then talk with Wayne. ");
textQuest5[0].push("Now let\'s move to the composition issue. In this land, there are 4 elements – Wind, Fire, Water and Earth. Each of them exists as crystal. We rank them as small, medium and large. We also have very rare stones – stone of blessing, stone of soul and holy stone. You can improve attack or even add additional attributes (fire, poison, thunder) to your weapons. You can also improve defence or add other attributes to your equipments and even as turn several small potions into a large one by composing the element crystals and stones together. Do you want to have a try?");
textQuest5[1].push("Here are 2 small crystals of fire and 1 stone of blessing. They can help add fire attribute to your weapon. Please hand them to Susan and she will help you complete the composition progress.");
textQuest5[2].push("No problem, please come to see me when you are not busy and I will tell you again.");
textQuest5[3].push("Composition completed? Well done young man! Now you own an unusual weapon! Composition is the best way to improve the abilities of your weapons and equipments. And it is a broad subject that is worthy of serious research! Oh, where to find the crystals and stones? You can get them randomly when you fight the monsters!");
textQuest5[4].push("Well, by now, I assume you have got some sense of this land. In the following days, please, help us find out what has happened to our village…");
textQuest5[5].push("Go to talk with Susan and she will help you with the composition progress.");
textQuest5[6].push("Weapon Composition (Main Quest)");
textQuest5[7].push("Go to talk with Susan, compose 2 small crystals of fire with Stone of Blessing to your weapon then go talk with Wayne. ");
textQuest6[0].push("I heard that you killed 10 Slimes, didn\'t you? Hehe, seems you are a little bit overproud. This land is not as easy as you imagined…innit? Ok, here I give you a mission - can you kill 20 level-7 wolves for me? If you end up as their next meal, don\'t come crying to me.");
textQuest6[1].push("Brave one. Go and show me how strong you are!");
textQuest6[2].push("As I expected…you need more practice to be a real adventurer.");
textQuest6[3].push("So, killing 20 level-7 wolves is that difficult for you? Hehe, so what are you proud of?");
textQuest6[4].push("Hehe, you came back in good condition. Not bad. A little bit more practice will get you as strong as my troops…Here\'s a pair of leather gloves. Take it if you want.");
textQuest6[5].push("Don\'t be Proud (Main Quest)");
textQuest6[6].push("Kill 20 lv.7 wolf then talk with Paul.");
textQuest7[0].push("Excuse me, can you help me? I have been making a kind of potion and asking the villagers to drink it, so they can more or less avoid attack from the monsters. This potion is made by honey but it has ran out. Before, my husband helped me get the honey from a purple hornet in the Rose Forest…Can you go to the Rose Forest on the east of this village and got me some? There is a specific spot in that forest where the purple hornet exists. My husband always went to get honey from it.");
textQuest7[1].push("Thank you! I\'m so happy that you can help me! Honey can be found in Rose Forest on the east of this village. The purple hrnet should be at the top-right of the forest!");
textQuest7[2].push("You don\'t have time? Ok…thank you all the same.");
textQuest7[3].push("Honey can be found on a purple hornet in the Rose Forest on the east of this village. The purple hornet is lacated at the top-right of the forest. Be careful, hornets are frenzy! You need to jump up to fight to them!");
textQuest7[4].push("Yes it is! This is such top-grade honey! This\'ll last a good while! Thank you very much indeed! This bracelet was left by my husband…Please take it!");
textQuest7[5].push("Susan\'s Honey (Main Quest)");
textQuest7[6].push("Find honey from the purple hornet in the Rose Forest on the east then give it to Susan.");
textQuest8[0].push("Have you heard about the Centaurs? They inhabit the west. They are very strong monsters. I heard that attaching 12 Centaur horns to the fencing surrounding the village can help protect the village from attack by the monsters!");
textQuest8[1].push("I want to do this for the village, but my capacity is limited! Can you go to the Goethe Grassland, fight with the centaurs and get me 12 Centaur horns?");
textQuest8[2].push("You deserve my admiration man! Centaurs are very ferocious, watch out! Don\'t go dying on me!");
textQuest8[3].push("What? Are you full of dread? Ok let\'s wait till you\'ve got enough courage!");
textQuest8[4].push("You came back! Wow! Look what you\'ve brought! 12 Centaur horns! You are a top warrior! I really value you! Here you are! This is the martial art book from my father. Read it and it should help you improve your skills!");
textQuest8[5].push("Have you got 12 Centaur horns? You can find the centaurs in the Goethe Grassland in the west.");
textQuest8[6].push("Horn of Courage (Main Quest)");
textQuest8[7].push("Help Kimura find 12 Centaur horns. ");
textQuest9[0].push("Bad news! Anna, the little girl with red hair, is missing!");
textQuest9[1].push("The last time I saw her, she was playing with her Teddy Bear. She said to the Teddy that she was going to the Sadness Forest to pick flowers while waiting for her parents to come back…It is too dangerous for her to go outside alone! Young man, can you help us bring her back please?");
textQuest9[2].push("Thank you! Please depart as soon as you can! The more time we waste, the more Anna\'s life hangs in the balance!");
textQuest9[3].push("Young man…please do help us find Anna!");
textQuest9[4].push("Anna! Where have you been…Thank goodness you have come back safely! Thank you young man! Thank you for bringing Anna back! Here is a large crystal of water, I hope it helps you become even more powerful!");
textQuest9[5].push("Have you found Anna?");
textQuest9[6].push("Missing of Anna (Main Quest)");
textQuest9[7].push("Go to the Sadness Forest and bring Anna back to Wayne.");
textQuest10[0].push("Although Anna is happy everyday, and everybody here treats me very well, I still want to see my mom and dad…or just hear some news about them…");
textQuest10[1].push("Mom and dad are the post deliverers for this village. Once they went to deliver letters in the south and never came back…I heard from the travellers that they had seen a couple who had lost their way in the Sadness Forest…Can you help Anna find her parents?? Or at least get some news about them, please??");
textQuest10[2].push("Thank you! If you find anything out about my mum and dad, please do tell me straight away! I\'ll be here waiting for your news!");
textQuest10[3].push("Oh…you can\'t help Anna?...");
textQuest10[4].push("You came back! Brought me any news?? Ah? You found my parents\' relic…? So they are dead…?...Anna\'s understood…Anna won\'t cry…Anna is a brave girl…(Weeping)…Anna will remember Mum and Dad\'s words: “Always be a good and happy girl my dear…”");
textQuest10[5].push("Thank you for bringing their belongings back and burying their bodies…Anna feels at ease now…These are my dad\'s boots. Take them if you please …");
textQuest10[6].push("Hi! Do you have any news about my mum and dad?");
textQuest10[7].push("End-result of Anna\'s Heart (Main Quest)");
textQuest10[8].push("Go to the Sadness Forest to look for tracks of Anna\'s parents.");
textQuest11[0].push("My man! Do you remember me telling you that I lost my ancestral sword, the Sword of Apollo, during the battle with Goblins at the Guilty Forest in south-east? That was the first time I had felt myself so close to death…I was scared and lost my courage…After that battle, in order to give myself a boost, I started boasting…");
textQuest11[1].push("I don\'t want to continue anymore…I want to be myself again! I want to wear my sword, but my capacity is not great enough for this…Could you please help me find both my sword and my courage?");
textQuest11[2].push("Thank you so much man! I look forward to hearing your good news!");
textQuest11[3].push("Ok…Please do help when you are not busy…I don\'t want to continue this decadent lifestyle.");
textQuest11[4].push("…You found it…! It\'s still in the same condition as before, no changes…! I thought it may be rusty…Even my sword hasn\'t changed, but is my courage rusted?");
textQuest11[5].push("No! I need to pull up my socks! Man! Thanks a lot for helping me get my courage back! I have decided to train myself hard and take up my duty as the village guard!");
textQuest11[6].push("I won\'t need this sword for a while, as it brought me too much pride and glory. I will start from the beginning! Here you go! I\'ll lend you the sword! Thanks again for helping me get my courage back! I hope I can catch up with you and fight together with you soon!");
textQuest11[7].push("Have you found my sword? Are those Goblins tough?");
textQuest11[8].push("Regain Courage (Main Quest)");
textQuest11[9].push("Get Kimura\'s sword back from the Guilty Forest in the South East.");
textQuest12[0].push("Hi! I\'ve got some good news! I have made a step forward in seeing again! After months of research, a new potion had been invented. If I can get back my eyes from the Centaurs, I can work out how to put them back and get them working again.");
textQuest12[1].push("I\'m begging for your help.. Please go to the Centaur Forest in the North West and recapture my eyes? To be able to see again is my greatest wish! Please help me!");
textQuest12[2].push("Thank you very much!! My eyes should be in the Centaur leader\'s hand. They live in the Centaur Forest in the North West. The leader is very vicious! Please be careful! Your life is more important than my eyes!");
textQuest12[3].push("Living in the dark and waking up with no hope…. These pains give me only one desire: to get my eyes back! Please help me!");
textQuest12[4].push("My instinct tells me you are bringing back exciting news! Yes! They are my eyes! Now…Let me try…Here\'s hoping for a miracle…");
textQuest12[5].push("......(After a flash, Susan\'s eyes opened…）......");
textQuest12[6].push("I can see! I can see you! Golden hair like sunshine, blue eyes like the ocean…I suffered in hopeless dark day after day and finally my sight is returned! Words do not exist to describe how grateful I am.");
textQuest12[7].push("These two bright Stones of Blessing were used to keep my eye sockets fresh and wet. I don\'t need them anymore. They can be used to process composition. Please take them! And thank you again!");
textQuest12[8].push("Do you have any news about my eyes? If you cannot defeat the Centaur leader, it is no problem for me to wait for a while…");
textQuest12[9].push("Re-see Brightness (Main Quest)");
textQuest12[10].push("Get Susan\'s eyes back from the Centaur Forest in the North West.");
textQuest13[0].push("You said you met a group from the Skeleton Army at the Valley of Rest in the South East and on their armour there was the Royal Army\'s badge?!...Oh my god…my poor Alan, Steve, Robert and David…my poor mates…! Who turned you into zombies and disturbed you from your rest?!");
textQuest13[1].push("Young warrior, they were my troops before. They all died in the battle with the Double-Headed Giant. I don\'t know who made them zombies by magic but, I can\'t bare their rest been disturbed…! Can you help me give these bodies one last blow and finally allow my friends the eternal peace they deserve?");
textQuest13[2].push("This is in fact a captain\'s responsibility, but my weak body makes me unable to do anything…I request your help…! Please help lay them to rest…");
textQuest13[3].push("Confused souls, when will you gain peace?");
textQuest13[4].push("…Is it?...I see…They laid down serenely? Great…I feel relieved now…(Weeping)…Oh god…Thank you for freeing them and resting them…Amen…This ring is a gift from the King. Please accept my appreciation…");
textQuest13[5].push("How\'s it going? Were they laid to rest…?");
textQuest13[6].push("Rest of the Souls (Main Quest)");
textQuest13[7].push("Help Paul give the skeleton knights in the Rest Valley one last decisive blow.");
textQuest14[0].push("Oh, there is one thing I haven\'t told anyone yet. During the battle with Double-Head Giant, he dropped an envelope. I put it in my pocket without him noticing.");
textQuest14[1].push("I have being so depressed in the last couple of months and never thought about it. Today I suddenly realised and checked it. The seal shows it was from Landlord Zack…! Why would Double-Head Giant have a letter from Zack?...I am worried this letter is related to the abnormity…Can you show it to Head Wayne and ask him to ensure whether this letter is really written by Zack?");
textQuest14[2].push("Good. Please come back to me after you\'ve got some information from Wayne.");
textQuest14[3].push("It is really a strange letter…I\'m not sure if Wayne will have anything to say about it…");
textQuest14[4].push("Paul asked you to show me this letter? Let me see…");
textQuest14[5].push("Ah! This really is Landlord Zack\'s signature! (Open the envelope and read) “Ask your men to protect the scroll in the Magic Cave…I will go to revive the Devil of Abyss in the dungeon…See you there! …Thanks for the immortality…”");
textQuest14[6].push("…What the hell is this? Why would Landlord Zack write to the monsters?! Why open the dungeon and revive the Devil of Abyss?...What is Landlord Zack doing?!...Young man, I don\'t know what\'s going on but I can confirm this letter was written by Landlord Zack! I am too familiar with his handwriting…!");
textQuest14[7].push("Please go discuss this with Paul and see what we should do next!");
textQuest14[8].push("Have you handed the letter to Wayne?");
textQuest14[9].push("Zack\'s Letter (Main Quest)");
textQuest14[10].push("Give the letter to Wayne to see if it is Zack\'s handwriting.");
textQuest15[0].push("Umm, now we can be sure this letter is from Zack…");
textQuest15[1].push("Immortality…? There is, indeed, a saying which goes something like: ‘He who revives Ssyba Devil of Abyss can obtain immortal life\'…So, the abnormity of this village does have something to do with Zack…");
textQuest15[2].push("But what is the scroll used for, the “scroll in the Magic Cave” in the letter?...It must have a hidden secret. Only if we get that scroll could we move closer to the heart of this torrid affair.");
textQuest15[3].push("The scroll is the most important clue right now. Only you have the capacity to get it back…There are many strong enemies in the cave…Are you ready to go?");
textQuest15[4].push("Right! The Magic Cave is to the North of the Centaur Forest. There are so many ferocious monsters. Please prepare yourself well before departing!");
textQuest15[5].push("Only if we got the scroll will we know what to do next. Time wait\'s for no man…");
textQuest15[6].push("Paul asked you to show me this letter? Let me see…");
textQuest15[7].push("Ah, is this the scroll mentioned in Zack\'s letter? Great! Let me see!...");
textQuest15[8].push("Umm…It was written in “Sacar” language…This old language has been lost for a very long time. It is rare to find people in this land who can read it …So our only clue is indecipherable? This is not the way things should be going…");
textQuest15[9].push("Zack can read the scroll for sure, as he knows many languages…But besides him, who else can read it? Let me see…");
textQuest15[10].push("Have you got the scroll? The Magic Cave is to the North of the Centaur Forest.");
textQuest15[11].push("The Old Scroll (Main Quest)");
textQuest15[12].push("Go get the Old Scroll in the Magic Cave to the North of Centaur Forest.");
textQuest16[0].push("Oh yes! Susan\'s eyes are fine now, aren\'t they? She is from another land and she knows many languages. She can read this! Can you take the scroll to Susan and see if she can help?");
textQuest16[1].push("Thanks! Come back to see me when you have some news.");
textQuest16[2].push("I assume Susan is the only one who may be able to read this language. She is our only hope now…");
textQuest16[3].push("Hi, what can I do for you? Yes? Old language? Let me see…Umm…it should be a language called Sacar which was lost for hundreds of years here on this land. Back in my land there was a similar language…I can try to translate it…");
textQuest16[4].push("mmm…The dungeon…Seal…Entrance…Village…Stela…Giant… Key…mmm…");
textQuest16[5].push("It says something like: The dungeon which the Devil of Abyss has been sealed in is inside Arcuz village. The entrance key is guarded by the Double-Headed Giant…It sounds like this won\'t be a simple job!");
textQuest16[6].push("A new challenge is waiting for you, my warrior…Hurry up and go tell this to Paul!");
textQuest16[7].push("Take the scroll to Susan and see if she can read it.");
textQuest16[8].push("The Truth (Main Quest)");
textQuest16[9].push("Ask Susan to translate the Old Scroll.");
textQuest17[0].push("Really? I got it…amazing news…! The dungeon where Devil of Abyss was sealed in is actually inside this village!...");
textQuest17[1].push("It seems the only thing to do is to defeat the Double-Headed Giant, get back the key and defend the entrance of the dungeon well so it can\'t be opened easily and evil won\'t come back to this land!");
textQuest17[2].push("But, whenever I recall the horror of Double-Headed Giant it makes me shudder…A whole team was wiped out by him in a flash…But you may defeat him as you have grown to be a capable warrior!");
textQuest17[3].push("When I was escaping from that tough battle with the Double-Headed Giant I used my last breath and sealed the entrance of the valley where the Double-Headed Giant lives. That seal can only be released by a special stone called “Nirvana”.");
textQuest17[4].push("This stone is very rare and can only be found in the Abandoned Mine in the South. But there will be some hard fighting waiting for you, as understrappers of the Double-Headed Giant must be searching for Nirvana as well! If they find the stone first…I don\'t even want to think about the consequences…! Are you ready to go?");
textQuest17[5].push("Great! Leave as quickly as you can! You can find Nirvana in the Abandoned Mine in the South! Take care!");
textQuest17[6].push("We have little time left…Please get yourself ready as soon as possible…");
textQuest17[7].push("You‘ve found Nirvana! Great! Only one more step to victory!");
textQuest17[8].push("Have you found the stone of Nirvana?");
textQuest17[9].push("Smash the Evil (Main Quest)");
textQuest17[10].push("Find the stone of Nirvana in the Abandoned Mine in the South.");
textQuest18[0].push("The seal at the entrance of the Valley can now be opened. It seems everything is working out…We are at about to pass through the storm before the calm!");
textQuest18[1].push("There are so many powerful monsters around the Double-Headed Giant. Don\'t look down on them…This will be the most difficult battle you have ever had…");
textQuest18[2].push("The fat lady doesn\'t sing until you defeat the Double-Headed Giant and get the key of the dungeon entrance…And then the land will return to peace again…");
textQuest18[3].push("Finally it will be over. All this can\'t be achieved without your help…I have never truly admired anyone until you my friend. The last battle... are you ready for it?...");
textQuest18[4].push("Before it\'s too late, please prepare well and get going! God be with you! I\'ll be waiting for your good news!");
textQuest18[5].push("This is far from being a simple mission…It\'s maybe a little bit difficult for you…Well…please get ready and come to see me again before it\'s too late…");
textQuest18[6].push("This is really a very difficult battle for a warrior like you. We will be praying for you…");
textQuest18[7].push("Song of the Valley (Main Quest)");
textQuest18[8].push("The final battle is at the deeper Rest Valley. Defeat the Double-headed Giant, get the key from the dungeon and bring peace to this land. ");
textSQuest1[0].push("I remember you said you are an adventurer? Cool, then you can definitely help me grab my goods back from the Goblins! Those damned Goblins hijacked my goods and killed the deliveryman at the North Forest when they were being shipped to the village! How evil those short and ugly things are!");
textSQuest1[1].push("If you can help me get my goods back, I will happily give you a load of money in commission! Ah? You ask me how much? Umm…I need to calculate with my abacus…anyway it won\'t be a small amount! Ok? You can help me?");
textSQuest1[2].push("Great! Time waits for no one! Please depart asap! Even if you have to risk your life I want my goods back!");
textSQuest1[3].push("I pay you, you help me, Isn\'t that fair??");
textSQuest1[4].push("What? You still haven\'t got my goods? I\'m really getting worried!");
textSQuest1[5].push("Wow! Am I dreaming? You defeated the Goblins! Yes, yes! Here are my goods! Wonderful! They are still in good condition! In order to thank you, I\'ll give you 1,000,000 gold then! …");
textSQuest1[6].push("Umm…let me see…1,000,000 gold sounds too much…Let\'s call it an awesome helmet then! This helmet is really very rare! Its sale price could be more than 1,000,000…! I\'m not joking! Here you are!");
textSQuest1[7].push("Robbed Goods (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest1[8].push("Get back Chung\'s goods from the Goblins in the North Forest.");
textSQuest2[0].push("Hey, it seems you\'re able to fight? Hum…it is too early for you to slay the dragon just like I did!");
textSQuest2[1].push("Right, let\'s make a bet: if you can kill 100 Slimes, I will give you my valuable waist belt! If you can\'t, you have to call me big brother forever! How about it? Dare to accept my challenge?");
textSQuest2[2].push("Hum! I have never lost a bet! Well, waiting for your “good” news then!");
textSQuest2[3].push("I know it is a mission impossible for you! Think....I killed 1,000 Slimes in 5 minutes! One of my super skills sent them all to hell!");
textSQuest2[4].push("Hahaha! Mission impossible for you? This sort of little case is as easy as blowing dust off a table for me!");
textSQuest2[5].push("Whaaat? You made it! Are....are you human? I just blundered out and thought it was mission impossible for you…! Man! You got my respect! Alright! I\'ll keep my word and give you my ancestral waist belt! Here you go!");
textSQuest2[6].push("Bet between Two Men (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest2[7].push("Kill 100 lv.1 Slimes in 5 minutes then show off in front of Kimura.");
textSQuest3[0].push("(Crying)…my best friend Teddy Bear is missing…Last time I went to play at the Silent Hill, I was tired and scared…then I lost it…");
textSQuest3[1].push("I can\'t stop fretting about it, but I\'m too afraid to tell anyone…as it\'s the birthday gift that all the villagers gave me…Can you help me look for it?...");
textSQuest3[2].push("(Crying)…Thank you!");
textSQuest3[3].push("(Crying)");
textSQuest3[4].push("(Crying)…Have you found my Teddy Bear…? I hope it is still on the Silent Hill…!");
textSQuest3[5].push("Whoa!! My Teddy Bear!! Thank you so much! I love you so much! Here! It\'s a beautiful stone I found! I\'m giving it to you!");
textSQuest3[6].push("Teddy Bear (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest3[7].push("Look for Anna\'s Teddy Bear at the Silent Hill.");
textSQuest4[0].push("Hey! How much do you have in your pocket? If you can save 3,000 gold for me, I will give you a superior falchion! It\'s such an awesome falchion with a lot of additional attributes! How about the deal? Do you want to experience the fun of saving money and buying luxury goods?");
textSQuest4[1].push("Hehe! Nice one! Well after you get 3,000 gold, come to see me anytime!");
textSQuest4[2].push("Don\'t you have the habit of saving? And you don\'t want to save money? Well if an economical crisis came about, how could you possible survive it? Cash is vital!");
textSQuest4[3].push("It seems saving money is not an easy thing for an adventure…Still haven\'t got 3,000 gold?");
textSQuest4[4].push("I heard music! The music of gold coins jingling! How sweet that melody is to my ears! Congrats! You will acquire the best weapon I have found in these times– The Assassin!");
textSQuest4[5].push("Purpose of Saving (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest4[6].push("Save 3,000 gold for Chung and you may get a brilliant weapon from him!");
textSQuest5[0].push("Hey! Can you help me? I want to make better weapons and armour! But I need better ironstone.I heard the highest quality ironstone is in the Mystery Cave on the north side. My grandfather used to use it! If you can find it for me I\'m sure my stuff will be improved a lot! Can you do me this favor?");
textSQuest5[1].push("Thanks a lot! There are monsters in the Mystery Cave! Be careful!");
textSQuest5[2].push("Ok…But I hope you can help me when you are not busy! Or you don\'t like helping me? Do you dislike me…!");
textSQuest5[3].push("You found the ironstone didn\'t you? It\'s in the Mystery Cave in the North. Watch out for the monsters!");
textSQuest5[4].push("What fantastic ironstone! You see! It\'s glinting! I can\'t wait to forge some awesome equipment! Thank you very much! You must take this gift!");
textSQuest5[5].push("Flickering Ironstone (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest5[6].push("Look for ironstone for Gran in the Mystery Cave in the north.");
textSQuest6[0].push("About composition, have you learnt anything? Several small potions can be composed to a medium one. Several medium ones can be turned into a large one. Let\'s try something practical. Can you make a large potion of rejuvenation for me? ");
textSQuest6[1].push("Great! Just treat it like chemistry homework. It is a good chance for you to learn more about composition.");
textSQuest6[2].push("This is really a good chance for you to research the rule of composition. It is a pity to give it up.");
textSQuest6[3].push("Several small potions can be composed into a medium one. Several medium ones can be turned into a large one. Composition is a profound subject. After a bit of trial and error you will work out the rule.");
textSQuest6[4].push("Not bad! It seems you have indeed got to grips with the rules of composition. These potions are the reward for your grade A homework!");
textSQuest6[5].push("Chemistry Lesson (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest6[6].push("Compose a large potion of rejuvenation for Susan.");
textSQuest7[0].push("Hey! Friend! I am working hard on forging new weapons! I made a shield called the Knight Shield! I want these attributes to be composed on it: Lv.2 Defense Bonus (%) and Lv.2 Chance of Block. Can you help me compose it?");
textSQuest7[1].push("Cheers! Please come to me when you\'ve completed it!");
textSQuest7[2].push("You don\'t want to help me? You don\'t like my craft?...");
textSQuest7[3].push("How about the shield composition? Have you come across any problems? I hope it is not my handcraft that has caused your trouble…!");
textSQuest7[4].push("Let me see…! Haha! Yes! This is the shield I want! See how perfect it is with the attributes attached! You really are a great composer!");
textSQuest7[5].push("Right! Take this shield for free, along with the just finished glove in the same set! I will keep going and make better stuff in the future!");
textSQuest7[6].push("Gran\'s Effort (Optional Quest)");
textSQuest7[7].push("Help Gran composing Lv.2 Defense Bonus (%) and Lv.2 Chance of Block shield");
